HUMAN BESTIARY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I enjoyed your article "Wild Things." However, I was disappointed by the 
exclusion of squirrels. 
</P>
<P>
As a resident of Los Feliz, I receive occasional visits from skunks, opossums, 
raccoons and coyotes, but my favorite is my squirrel friend who scratches on my 
window to remind me to leave a supply of nuts every morning. 
</P>
<P>
Unfortunately, she is spied upon by a blue jay who follows her and steals most 
of the nuts she buries. 
</P>
<P>
GARY A. ROBB 
