HIGH SCHOOL ROUNDUP; 
</P>
<P>
BLYLEVEN OUTSHINES MOFFAT, 1-0 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Andy Moffat of Newbury Park High pitched a three-hitter but was outdueled by 
Todd Blyleven, the son of Angel pitcher Bert Blyleven, in Villa Park's 1-0 
victory in the consolation championship game of the Loara tournament Saturday 
at Glover Stadium in Anaheim. 
</P>
<P>
