with Ballet Pacifica since his retirement. JOHN FUNG / Los Angeles Times; 
Photo, Cornell Maier BONNIE KAMIN / Los Angeles Times; Photo, One of Ed Akins' 
model doll houses. ; Photo, Ed Akins used to build full-sized homes in Orange 
County. Now he builds detailed scale models. MARK BOSTER / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
