<P>
THE WORD IS OPA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
We were very pleased by Sylvia Steinberg's Reader Recommendation ("Jerry 
Hulse's Travel Tips," Feb. 18). However, the name of our company is OPA Tours 
Greece, not OTA Tours. The word opa is Greek; it's what the Greek people say 
when they are having a wonderful time. 
</P>
<P>
JOYCE HELFAND 
</P>
<P>
OPA TOURS GREECE 
</P>
<P>
Tujunga 
